{"tid":343242,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣趕走籃球場打板球既蝻 ?","createTime":"2017-08-01T09:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T17:09:44.000Z","uid":47584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1997ab0208c831d61282d66feddba6296b27d453","tid":343242,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/173759_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F173759_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=230f8c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖<br />\n啲仆街蝻工細路好撚鍾意喺籃球場打板球<br />\n<br />\n原本個場都有啲家長帶小朋友嚟打親子籃球<br />\n我同啲家長都試過開聲趕啲蝻走<br />\n不過啲蝻冇理到<br />\n最後班家長驚個波打中個細路就走左 (個波雖然細，但打中皮膚會好撚痛，中過就知)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報唔報得警 ?"},{"pid":"05540b6f6b113c7adba1fb99c994f5a067208756","tid":343242,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"拿. 板球都要有個波先打得成, 佢地一打遠個波你就偷偷地...."},{"pid":"bee714a3a62b841df9e32979e09c99bb2d560969","tid":343242,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"報警搞掂"},{"pid":"9e174fc8fe1dc1124185b32309792ce2da55b1fa","tid":343242,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"一個籃球扔落去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申淆底"},{"pid":"84c4582a14c10153bdb3f1e8dce42de134c637a7","tid":343242,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"我地南亞人做錯咩要俾你地迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2667c56898eb373a165f77946adf5f111d70ec8","tid":343242,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"報警 話佢打中人"},{"pid":"fba09f2de28204275dbc8dda7acdd50b8ec10cff","tid":343242,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":